{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Infest is a roguelike deckbuilder where every pixel on the battlefield can burn, freeze, corrode, shock, and melt. Carefully craft your deck and deploy cards to alter the environment, buff your stats, and unleash stunning pixel-by-pixel damage upon your enemies! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Turn-based battle combined with realtime physics. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fire, Oil, Ice, Poison Gas, Water, Seeds and Growing Plants are just a few of the elements you'll have to strategically navigate.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341560/extras/g1-595.gif?t=1737648147\" /><i>(A pixel chain reaction after deploying a LightningCard)</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your deck and upgrade cards along the way. Make sure it is well balanced to handle a variety of environmental effects. Can you melt ice? Can you stop mutant plants? Foresight is key. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deal damage card by card, when your stack is exhausted the enemies get their chance to attack! They will create defensive barriers, throw damage cards at you, buff themselves and heal others! Anticipating their moves and playing the right card is key. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341560/extras/g2-595.gif?t=1737648147\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your path through the alien universe. Each run is different so you can replay many times without getting bored. Besides the playable levels, you'll encounter shops, hospitals, and dozens of different bonus challenges. Picking the right path is key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixel by pixel simulated physics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roguelite style permadeath</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dozens of side-rooms, shops, hospitals, mini-challenges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dozens of playable cards, perks, and items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dozens of playable levels with procedural generation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Advanced tech tree for leveling up cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Achievements and Steam Cloud</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"World 1 Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/f4a2e6b2465386224b0e71345e8d3ef9f8a1273f.jpg"},{"name":"World 2 Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/4a8fe61c638d141278320c4c3c7891112b38ef0c.jpg"},{"name":"World 3 Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/16c20b39000b49e141adfdb671ba113e1fadf373.jpg"},{"name":"Card Upgrade Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/30ddc7fa680c2b95903ecf63030641abf257781e.jpg"},{"name":"Target Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/dc8d1ac2082b343e5da69aff3e47a34e84e111fb.jpg"},{"name":"Target Card","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/c9adfdf38513b6640013fb7f0c2cd72658cefd36.jpg"},{"name":"Single Card Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/9d9184a1f4ad35b87349489d2107e6b842a4cde0.jpg"},{"name":"Tutorial Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/e8e7251e224fd22e0bfce2690d57be746561ec89.jpg"},{"name":"Infest Level 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341560/830aeb4ff155eee009767cb888dfaa72cb8887d9.jpg"},{"name":"Infest Level 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images